              <text>Section 66(c) is amended by adding <amend.in quote="1">, except that the reference in <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">subsection (2)(a)</citation></changeable> to whether the parties wish to resume or continue the marriage or de facto relationship must be read as a reference to whether the parties to the parenting order (or the agreement), or the 2 or more guardians, have resolved the dispute</amend.in>.</text>
